    <h1 class="display">
      Let's <span class="accent">recalibrate</span>.
    </h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Tlali, Micha, Kim — I've been heads-down on GritFuel for the past few weeks and the foundations have moved. This site walks you through what shifted, why, and the calls I need the four of us to make together before we go live.
    </p>
  </div>
  <img class="hero-arrow" src="assets/brand-assets/arrow-charcoal.png" alt="">
