      <p>Each section runs ~8–12 minutes. The narrative and the decisions are the core; the artefacts are for when you want to go deeper.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="themes">
      <a class="theme-card t-strategy" href="01-strategy.html">
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
