      <a class="theme-card t-gtm" href="05-gtm.html">
        <div class="accent-bar"></div>
        <span class="num">05 / GTM</span>
        <span class="title">GTM</span>
        <p class="desc">Assumption-to-tactic map, PMF &amp; positioning note, and the onboarding flow — how we translate all of this into a first cohort.</p>
        <span class="count">3 artefacts · ~8 min</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What I need --------------------------------------------------------- -->
<section class="band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What I'd like from you</span>
      <h2>Read, react, recalibrate.</h2>
    </div>

    <ol class="steps" style="max-width: 820px;">
      <li>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>First pass — skim all five overviews (~25 min)</h4>
          <p>Just the narrative + decision blocks on each section page. Don't open artefacts yet. Get a sense of where things have moved.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Second pass — open the artefacts in your lane</h4>
          <p>Tlali — Strategy + GTM. Micha — Product + Finance. Kim — Brand + GTM. Click through the live tools. Poke at anything that feels off.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Reply with reactions — not edits</h4>
          <p>Each section ends with two or three specific questions. Hit those first. Everything else — free-form — welcome in the same reply.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>We meet to close the open calls</h4>
          <p>Once all three of you have replied, we do a 60–90 min working session to resolve anything still open before go-live on 29 April.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

